Package: libphpcassa-php5
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, ${php:Depends}, php5 (>= 5.3)
Description: PHP client library for Apache Cassandra
 phpcassa allows interactions with and queries to an Apache Cassandra cluster
 from the PHP language.
 .
 This version is compatible with Cassandra 0.7, 0.8, 1.0, and 1.1

